{
  "page": "Feature quote/275",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“They call me Baelon the Brave, but you are far braver than me. I would sooner fight a dozen battles than do what you've just done.” —Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a><br />“You were made for battles, and I was made for this. <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Baelon)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Baelon)\">Aegon</a>, that's three. As soon as I am well, let's make another. I want to give you twenty sons. An army of your own!” —Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Targaryen\" title=\"Alyssa Targaryen\">Alyssa Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404073926\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 10